flowchart LR
  subgraph S1[Define Constraints]
    A[1<br/>Documentation First<br/>Understand Existing Code + Design Plan]
    B[2<br/>UX / API Draft<br/>Prototype Design / API Contract]
    C[3<br/>Test Framework<br/>Define Success Criteria]
    A --> B --> C
  end
  C --> D{Need More<br/>Constraints?}
